<subSubSection id="15DE5FE0FFA5EF66FF42F892FDFBF84D" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="5D7B0C6BFFA5EF66FF42F892FA35F869" blockId="13.[151,1437,1758,2038]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis id="6FB0D079FFA5EF66FF42F892FEE7F8F9" bold="true" box="[199,338,1831,1857]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Comments:</emphasis>
The description of this species brings 
<collectingCountry id="25D34CFBFFA5EF66FD78F892FCF4F8F9" box="[765,833,1831,1857]" name="Brazil" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Brazil</collectingCountry>
<materialsCitation id="EDAC0636FFA5EF66FCCDF89DFAC9F869" collectionCode="OSF" country="Argentina" location="This" municipality="Iguacu Falls" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" specimenCount="2">
as its 
<typeStatus id="827FB2C9FFA5EF66FC03F89DFC03F8FA" box="[902,950,1832,1858]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">type</typeStatus>
locality, and this species is recorded for the first time since its original description. All species of this genus have a very elongated fastigium, generally longer than the length of the pronotal disc. The individual collected here has a bright green colour, different from the 
<typeStatus id="827FB2C9FFA5EF66FAE0F8C5FA2DF832" box="[1381,1432,1904,1930]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">type</typeStatus>
, where the colour has probably deteriorated (photos available on 
<collectionCode id="3BD594AEFFA5EF66FCE0F826FC2DF815" box="[869,920,1939,1965]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">OSF</collectionCode>
database). 
<location id="581B5AB0FFA5EF66FB93F826FBFDF815" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:D56DBD7DFFA5EF66FF12F9C6FDFBF84D:581B5AB0FFA5EF66FB93F826FBFDF815" box="[1046,1096,1939,1965]" country="Argentina" municipality="Iguacu Falls" name="This" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">This</location>
specimen was collected in the buildings close to the 
<collectingMunicipality id="BD1F9611FFA5EF66FE08F80DFDACF869" box="[397,537,1975,2002]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Iguaçu Falls</collectingMunicipality>
, so the species is also possibly present in the homonymous park in 
<collectingCountry id="25D34CFBFFA5EF66FA8CF802FAC9F869" box="[1289,1404,1975,2001]" name="Argentina" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Argentina</collectingCountry>
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5D7B0C6BFFA5EF66FF42F86EFDFBF84D" blockId="13.[151,1437,1758,2038]" box="[199,590,2011,2038]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
